params.initialGas: the initial amount of gas that should be used as a baseline to charge the single fulfillment for execution cost
params.reportValidationGas: the amount of gas used for the report validation. Cost is split by all fulfillments on the report.
params.requestId: identifier for the request that was generated by the Registry in the beginBilling commitment
params.signerCount: the number of signers on the report
params.signers: the Oracles who had a part in generating the report
params.transmitter: the Oracle who sent the report
